                <span class="badge bg-white text-primary px-3 py-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-briefcase me-1"></i> Job Matching
                </span>
                <span class="badge bg-white text-primary px-3 py-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-video me-1"></i> Interview Scheduling
